OL,3,CCouncillors warn of abuse at public
OL,4,Cmeetings
OL,6,FTwo councillors in the Borders say
OL,7,Fthey have been shouted at and
OL,8,Fthreatened by members of the public at
OL,9,Fcommunity meetings.
OL,11,FCouncillor Viv Thomson and Councillor
OL,12,FDrummond Begg represent the Tweeddale
OL,13,FWest ward on Scottish Borders Council.
OL,15,FCouncillor Thomson, SNP, said: "People
OL,16,Fwill talk over you, they will shout at
OL,17,Fyou, they will lean in and point and
OL,18,Fit's behaviour that you wouldn't
OL,19,Faccept in any other sphere."
