OL,6,FCouncillor Begg, Scottish Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats, said: "It's almost a normal
OL,8,Fthing now for people to say, well if
OL,9,Fyou go into politics you can expect to
OL,10,Fbe abused, you can expect to be
OL,11,Fthreatened, and that is not a good job
OL,12,Fdescription."
OL,14,FCouncillor Thomson says attitudes
OL,15,Ftowards women have gone backwards.
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@MO]
