OL,3,CCouncillors warn of abuse at public
OL,4,Cmeetings
OL,6,F"I do feel that behaviours towards
OL,7,Ffemales have changed again and for me
OL,8,Fit's gone back to the behaviours of
OL,9,Fthe eighties. You made more comment
OL,10,Fabout what they were wearing than what
OL,11,Fthey were saying and I think we're
OL,12,Fback to that kind of level. We are
OL,13,Fmoving away from everybody's
OL,14,Fcontribution being valued."
OL,16,FCouncillor Begg, who also works as a
OL,17,FGP, says the abuse is part of the
OL,18,Freason he won't be standing for
OL,19,Felection again.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@[O]
