OL,3,CCouncillors warn of abuse at public
OL,4,Cmeetings
OL,6,FAt an event held today in Edinburgh,
OL,7,Felected politicians met with police
OL,8,Fofficers, government ministers and
OL,9,Fexperts from the third sector, to
OL,10,Fdiscuss how to address the issue. An
OL,11,Faction plan is expected to be
OL,12,Fpublished in the coming weeks.
